From 8303b71a8df64094a7e97a2747145fd6dc92811e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Piotr Gorski <lucjan.lucjanov@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 2 Jul 2026 14:22:42 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] sched-7.1: introduce Infinity Scheduler by Galih Tama

Signed-off-by: Piotr Gorski <lucjan.lucjanov@gmail.com>
---
